    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<strong>Magnetron Rebellion: Fully Loaded</strong> is a top-down shooter inspired by classics like Galaga with a major twist: you must use the enemy's bullets against them! Your ship is equipped with a powerful magnet capable of capturing the enemy bullets and firing them back at them! Just be warned, attempt to capture too many bullets at once and your magnet will be overloaded, unable to stop further bullets.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Master several levels filled with enemies all gunning to crush the rebellion!<br></li><li> Use the various types of enemy munitions to turn the tide of battle. Hitting a ship with the matching color will deal double damage!<br></li><li> Compete for the high score!  Scores are uploaded to the Steam Leaderboard so you can brag to your friends!<br></li><li> Go the distance in Endless mode! Waves keep spawning so survive as long as you can!<br></li><li> Colorblind accessibility - change the color of the enemy ships to easily identify each type at a glance.</li></ul>",
